Package: focusde
Version: @VERSION@
Section: x11
Priority: optional
Architecture: all
Depends: sway, waybar, fuzzel, foot, greetd, python3, python3-gi, python3-gi-cairo, gir1.2-gtk-3.0, gir1.2-gtk-4.0, fluidsynth, fluid-soundfont-gm
Recommends: abiword, gnumeric, firefox-esr, ffmpeg
Maintainer: Stéphane Weg <steph.wegener@gmail.com>
Homepage: https://github.com/stephaneweg/FocusDE
Description: Focus DE — activity-based Sway desktop
 An activity-based Linux desktop on Sway (pastel, borderless look) that hosts
 real applications inside tabbed, split activities. Ships the activity shell
 (activities, applets, panel, theme), a greetd login session, and the FM-Song
 MIDI tracker. Defaults install into /etc/skel so every new user gets it.
